  %% 图3.3 系统总体架构图（黑白版）

  subgraph Client[客户端]
    Web[Web/移动端前台\nVue 3 + Pinia + Router]
    Admin[管理端前台\nVue 3（管理入口）]
    Device[扫码设备端\n（设备UID + 核销）]
  end

  subgraph Server[服务端]
    API[REST API\nSpring Boot\nController/Service/Mapper]
    WS[WebSocket\n实时推送]
    Upload[文件上传\nMultipart（报修图片）]
  end

  subgraph Storage[数据与中间件]
    MySQL[(MySQL\n业务数据)]
    Redis[(Redis\n缓存/临时状态)]
    File[(文件存储\n本地/对象存储)]
  end

  Web -->|HTTP/JSON| API
  Admin -->|HTTP/JSON| API
  Device -->|HTTP/JSON| API

  Web <--> |WebSocket| WS
  Admin <--> |WebSocket（可选）| WS

  API -->|读写| MySQL
  API -->|缓存访问| Redis
  Upload -->|保存文件| File
  API -->|保存元信息| MySQL

  %% 黑白打印风格
  classDef node fill:#FFFFFF,stroke:#111111,stroke-width:1px,color:#111111;
  classDef group fill:#FFFFFF,stroke:#666666,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 4 3,color:#111111;
  class Web,Admin,Device,API,WS,Upload,MySQL,Redis,File node;
  class Client,Server,Storage group;

